hadiths[147]{hadithnumber,text}:
6805,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah farmata hai : mere barey mein mera banda jo guman karta hai main ( usko pura karne ke liye) uske paas hota hun. jab wo mujhey yad karta hai to main iske sath hota hun. agar wo mujhey apne dil mein yad karta hai to main usey dil mein yad karta hun aur agar wo mujhey ( bhari ( majlis mein yad karta hai to main unki majlis se achi majlis mein usey yad karta hun, agar wo aik baalisht mere qareeb aata hai to main aik hath iske qareeb jata hun aur agar wo aik hath mere qareeb aata hai to main donon hathon ki poori lambai ke barabar iske qareeb aata hun, agar wo mere paas chalta hua aata hai to main daudta hua uske paas jata hun."
6806,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur unhon-ne ye bayan nahi kya ke agar wo aik hath mere qareeb aata hai to main donon hathon ki poori lambai ke barabar uske qareeb aata hun."
6807,"hamein Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadison Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha : Allah Taala ne farmaya : jab banda aik baalisht ( badh kar) mere paas aata hai to main aik hath ( badh kar) uske paas jata hun aur jab wo aik hath ( badh kar) mere paas aata hai to main donon hathon ki lambai ke barabar ( badh kar) uske paas jata hun aur agar wo donon hathon ki lambai ke barabar badh kar mere paas aata hai to main uske paas pahunch jata hon, us se zyada tezi se aata hun."
6808,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka ke aik rastey par chaley ja rahe they ke aap ka aik pahaad ke qareeb se guzar hua jis ko jamdaan kaha jata hai, aap ne farmaya : chaltey raho, ye Jumdaan hai. mufarridun (logon se alag ho kar tanha ho janey waale) bazi ley gaey. logon ne puchha : Allah ke rasool! mufarridun se kya murad hai? farmaya : kasarat se Allah ko yad karne waley (mard) aur Allah ko yad karne wali (auratein.)"
6809,"Amr Naqid, Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Amr ke hain. padhi. unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu-Zinad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ke ninyaanwe naam hain, jisne unki hifazat ki wo jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyga aur Allah witr ( taaq ( hai, witr ko pasand karta hai. aur ibne-abi-Umar ki riwayat mein hai : jisne unko shumaar kya."
6810,"Mamar ne hamein Ayub se khabar di, unhon-ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, neez ( Ayub ne) Hammam-bin-Munabba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ke ninyaanwe, aik kam so naam hain, jisne un (sab) ko shumaar kya wo jannat mein dakhil hoga aur Hammam ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se mazeed ye bayan kya be-shak wo ( Allah ( taaq hai, taaq hi ko pasand karta hai."
6811,"Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tak tum mein se koi shakhs dua karey to qataeyat ke sath (israar kartey huey) dua karey aur ye na kahey : aey Allah! agar to chahey to mujhey de dey, kyonke Allah ko majbur karne wala koi nahi hai."
6812,"Alaa ke walid ( Abdur-Rehman ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs dua karey to ye na kahey : aey Allah! agar to chahey to mujhey bakhsh de, balke wo pukhtagi aur israar se sawal karey aur badi raghbat ka izhar karey, kyonke dene ke liye Allah Taala ke liye koi cheez badi nahi hai."
6813,"Ata-bin Mina ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs is tarah na kahey : aey Allah ! agar to chahey to mujhey bakhsh de, aey Allah! agar to chahey to mujh par raham farma. wo dua mein pukhtagi aur qataeyat se kaam ley kyonke Allah jo chahey wahi karta hai, koi nahi jo usey majbur kar sakey."
6814,"Abdul-Azeez ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs kisi nuqsan (museebat) ki wjah se, jo is par nazil ho, maut ki tamanna na kare. agar us ne laa-muhaala maut maangni bhi ho to yun kahey : aey Allah ! mujhey us waqt tak zinda rakh jab tak zindagi mere liye behtar ho aur mujhey wafat de jab maut mere liye behtar ho."
6815,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : kisi nuqsan ki wjah se jo usey pahunchey. (nazil ho nahi kaha)"
6816,Aasim ne hamein nazar bin Anas se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) un dinon zinda they. ( nazar ne) kaha : Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya na hota : tum mein se koi shakhs maut ki tamanna na karey to main maut ki tamanna karta.
6817,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Ismail bin abi Khalid se, unhon-ne Qais-bin abi Hazim se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey, us waqt unke pet par (ilaaj ke liye) saat jagah (tapti hui dhaat se) dagh lagaey gaey they. unhon-ne kaha : agar ye na hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein maut ki dua se mana farmaya tha, to main us (maut) ki dua karta."
6818,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Jarir bin abdul-hameed, Wakee, Abdullah-bin-Numair, Motamir bin Sulaiman aur abu-Usama sab ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath (yahi) riwayat ki."
6819,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadison hamein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye ( bhi) thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs hargiz maut ki tamanna na karey, na maut aaney se pahley uske liye dua karey kyonke jab tum mein se koi shakhs mar gaya to uska amal munqata ho gaya (mazeed amal ki mohlat khatm ho gai) aur momin ki umr uski bhalai hi mein izafa karti hai."
6820,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah se milney ko mahboob rakhey, Allah us se milney ko mehbub rakhta hai aur jo Allah se milney ko na-pasand karey, Allah bhi us se milney ko na-pasand karta hai."
6821,"Shoba ne Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6822,"Khalid-bin Haris Hujaimi ne kaha : hamein Saeed ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne zuraarah se, unhon-ne Sad bin Hisham se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko pasand karey, Allah us se mulaqat ko pasand farmata hai aur jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko na-pasand karey, Allah us se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai. maine kaha : Allah ke Nabi! kya us se maut ki na-pasandidgi murad hai? ham mein se har shakhs (taban) maut ko na-pasand karta hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye baat nahi hai, lekin jab momin ko Allah ki rehmat, uski razaamandi aur jannat ki basharat di jati hai to wo Allah se mulaqat ko pasand karta hai aur kaafir ko jab Allah ke azab aur uski naaraazagi ki khabar di jati hai to wo Allah se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai aur Allah bhi us ( naa-shukrey aur mutakabbir ( se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai."
6823,Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne kaha : hamein Saeed ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
6824,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Zakariya se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Shureh bin Hani se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko pasand karta hai, Allah us se mulaqat ko pasand karta hai aur jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai, Allah bhi us se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai aur maut Allah ki mulaqat se pahley hai. ( mulaqat ka mamla iske baad aayega .)"
6825,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne kaha : hamein Zakariya ne Aamir (Shabi) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey shuraih bin Hani ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, usi (guzishta riwayat) ki tarah ."
6826,"absar ne Mutarrif se, unhon-ne Aamir se, unhon-ne shureh-bin-Hani se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko pasand karey, Allah us se mulaqat ko pasand karta hai aur jo Allah se mulaqat ko na-pasand karey, Allah us se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai. (shureh-bin-Hani ne) kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas hazir hua aur kaha : Ummul-Momenin ! maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik hadis bayan kartey huey suna, agar wo isi tarah hai (jis tarah wo bayan kartey hain) to ham halaak ho gaey. to unhon (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne farmaya : halaak honey wala waqei wahi hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qaul se halaak hua. ( bataao ( wo kya hadis hai? ( maine kaha : ( unhon-ne kaha hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko pasand karta hai Allah bhi us se mulaqat ko pasand karta hai aur jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai, Allah bhi us se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai aur ham mein aisa koi nahi jo maut ko na-pasand na karta ho. to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya tha, lekin (mafhoom ke eitibaar se) jis taraf tum gaey ho wo baat is tarah nahi balke (wo is tarah hai ke) jab nigaah uper ki taraf uth jati hai aur seeney mein saans ukhad rahi hoti hai aur jild par raungtey khadey ho jatey hain aur ungliyan tedhii ho kar akad jati hain to us waqt jo Allah se milney ko pasand karta hai, Allah bhi us se milnaa pasand karta hai. aur jo (us waqt) Allah se mulaqat ko na-pasand karta hai, Allah bhi us se milnaa na-pasand karta hai."
6827,Jarir ne Mutarrif se isi sanad ke sath absar ki hadis ki tarah khabar di.
6828,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko pasand karey, Allah bhi us se mulaqat ko pasand karta hai aur jo shakhs Allah se mulaqat ko na-pasand karey, Allah bhi us se milney ko na-pasand karta hai."
6829,"Yazeed-bin-Asamm ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : mera banda mere barey mein jo guman karta hai, main ( usko pura karne ke liye) uske paas hota hun aur jab wo mujhey pukarta hai to main uske sath hota hun."
6830,"Yahya-bin-Saeed aur ibne-abi-Adi ne Sulaiman Taimi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah farmata hai : jab mera banda aik baalisht mere qareeb aata hai to main aik hath uske qareeb aata hun. aur jab wo aik hath mere qareeb aata hai to main donon hathon ki lambai ke barabar uske qareeb aata hun. aur jab wo chal kar mere paas aata hai to main daud kar uske paas jata hun."
6831,Moatamir ne apne walid (Sulaiman Taimi) se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur jab wo chal kar mere paas aata hai to main daud kar uske paas jata hun zikr nahi kiya.
6832,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah farmata hai : mera banda mere barey mein jo guman karta hai to main ( usko pura karne ke liye) uske paas hota hun. aur jab wo mujhey yad karta hai to main uske sath hota hon, agar wo mujhey apne dil mein yad karta hai to main usey apne dil mein yad karta hun. agar wo mujhey kisi majlis mein yad karta hai to main un logon ki majlis se behtar majlis mein usko yad karta hun. aur agar wo aik baalisht mere qareeb hota hai to main aik hath uske qareeb ho jata hon, agar wo aik hath mere qareeb hota hai to main phailey huey donon hathon ki lambai jitna ( fasla ( uske qareeb ho jata hun. aur agar wo chal kar meri taraf aata hai to main daud kar uske paas aata hun."
6833,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ma'roor-bin-Suwed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah farmata hai : jo shakhs aik neki lekar aata hai, usey us jaisi das milti hain aur main badha (bhi) deta hun. aur jo shakhs burai lekar aata hai to uska badla us jaisi aik burai hai ya (chaahoon to) maaf kar deta hun. jo aik baalisht mere qareeb hota hai to main aik hath uske qareeb ho jata hun aur jo aik hath mere qareeb hota hai to main do hathon ke phailaao jitna uske qareeb ho jata hun. aur jo mere paas chalta hua aata hai, main uske paas daudta hua jata hun. aur jo mujh se poori zamin ki wusat bhar gunahon ke sath mulaqat karta hai (aur) mere sath kisi cheez ko Sharik nahi thahrata, main itni hi maghfirat ke sath us se mulaqat karta hun. (Imam Muslim ke shagird ( Ibrahim ne kaha : ham se Hasan-bin-Bishr ne, unko Wakee ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
6834,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : uske liye us jaisi das nekiyan milti hain, ya main (is se bhi) zyada deta hun."
6835,"Muhammad-bin-abu-Adi ne Humaid se, unhon-ne Sabit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon mein se aik aisey shakhs ki iyaadat ki jo laaghir ho kar choozey ki tarah ho gaya tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : kya tum Allah Taala se kisi cheez ki dua kartey they ya us se kuchh maangtey they? usne kaha : ji haan , main kehta tha : aey Allah ! to mujhey aakhirat mein jo saza dene wala hai abhi duniya hi mein de dey. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah paak hai ! tum mein uski taqat nahi hai. ya ( farmaya : ( tum uski istitaat nahi rakhtey. tum ne ye kyon na kaha : aey Allah ! hamein duniya mein bhi achchhai ata farma aur aakhirat mein bhi achchhai ata farma aur hamein aag ke azab se bacha ley. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye Allah se dua farmai to usne is shakhs ko shifa ata farma di."
6836,Khalid-bin-Haaris ne kaha : hamein Humaid ne isi sanad ke sath dua ki in alfaz tak hadis bayan ki : hamein dozakh ke azab se bacha aur us se izaafi baat bayan nahi ki.
6837,"Hammad ne kaha : Sabit ne hamein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba mein se aik shakhs ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif le gaey, wo choozey ki tarah ( laaghir (ho gaya tha. iske baad Humaid ki hadis ke ham mana hai, magar unhon-ne is tarah kaha : tum mein Allah ka azab bardasht karne ki taqat nahi. unhon-ne ye bayan nahi kiya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye Allah se dua ki to usne is shakhs ko shifa ata farma di."
6838,Qatada ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki.
6839,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : Allah tabarak w taala ke kuchh Farishtey hain jo (Allah ki zamin mein) chakkar lagaatey rahtey hain. wo Allah ke zikr ki majlisein talash kartey hain. jab wo koi aisi majlis patey hain jis mein (Allah ka ( zikr hota hai to unke sath baith jatey hain, wo aik doosrey ko apne paron se is tarah dhanp letey hain ke apne aur duniya ke aasman ke darmyan (ki wusat ko) bhar detey hain. jab ( majlis mein Sharik hone-waale ( log muntashir (bikhar) ho jatey hain to ye ( Farishtey ( bhi uper ki taraf jatey hain aur aasman par chaley jatey hain, kaha : to izzat aur jalaal waala Allah unse poochhta hai, halanke wo unke barey mein sabse zyada jaanney wala hai : tum kahan se aaey ho? wo kehtey hain : ham zamin main ( rehney waale) terey bandon ki taraf se (ho kar) aaey hain jo teri pakeezgi bayan kar rahe they, teri badaai keh rahe they aur sirf aur sirf terey hi maabood honey ka iqrar kar rahe they aur teri hamd aur sana kar rahe they aur tujhii se maang rahe they. farmaya : wo mujh se kya maang rahe they? unhon-ne kaha : wo aap se aap ki jannat maang rahe they. farmaya : kya unhon-ne meri jannat dekhi hai? unhon-ne kaha : parwardigar ! ( unhon-ne ( nahi ( dekhi ). farmaya : agar unhon-ne meri jannat dekhi hoti kya hota ! (kaisey ro-ro kar aur gid-gida kar maangtey ! ( wo kehtey hain : aur wo teri panah maang rahe they, farmaya : wo kis cheez se meri panah maang rahe they? unhon-ne kaha : teri aag (jahannam ( se, aey rab! farmaya : kya unhon-ne meri aag (jahannam) dekhi hai? unhon-ne kaha : aey rab ! nahi ( dekhi ( , farmaya : agar wo meri jahannam dekh letey to ( unka kya haal hota ! ( wo kehtey hain : wo tujh se gunahon ki bakhshish maang rahe they, to wo farmata hai : maine unke gunah bakhsh diye aur unhon-ne jo maanga maine unhein ata kar diya aur unhon-ne jis se panah mangi maine unhein panah de di. ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : wo ( Farishtey ( kehtey hain : parwardigar ! unmein falan shakhs bhi maujood tha, sakht gunahgaar banda , wahan se guzartey huey unke sath baith gaya tha. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : to Allah irshad farmata hai : maine usko bhi bakhsh diya. ye aisey log hain ke unki wjah se unke sath baith janey wala bhi mahroom nahi rehta."
6840,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Suhaib ne kaha : Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kon si dua kasarat se maanga kartey they? Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kasarat se jo dua maanga kartey they wo ye thi ke aap kehtey : aey Allah ! hamein duniya mein bhi achchhai ata farma, aakhirat mein bhi acchhhai ata farma aur hamein aag ke azab se mehfooz rakh. kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) jab koi aik dua maangna chahtey to yahi dua maangtey aur jab badi dua maangna chahtey to usmein ye dua bhi maangtey."
6841,Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( dua farmatey huey ye ( kaha kartey they : aey hamarey rab ! hamein duniya mein bhi achchhai ata farma aur aakhirat mein bhi achchhai ata farma aur hamein dozakh ke azab se bacha.
6842,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs din mein sau martaba :                                                                                                                                                  (لا اله الا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله لحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير)                                                                                                             '' Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa hai, uska koi Sharik nahi, saari badhshahat usi ki hai, hamd sirf usi ke layeq hai aur wahi har cheez par qaadir hai.''                                                                                                                            kahey: us shakhs ko das ghulam aazad karne ke barabar ajr milta hai, uske liye so nekiyan likhi jati hain, uske sau gunah mitaa diye jatey hain aur ye kalimaat Sham tak pura din shaitan se uski hifazat ka zariya bin jati hain aur koi shakhs is se zyada afzal amal nahi kar sakta , siwaey us shakhs ke jo us se bhi zyada martaba yahi amal karey aur jis shakhs ne aik din mein sau martaba (سبحان الله وبحمده) kaha to iske tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, chahey wo samandar ke jhaag ke barabar hon."
6843,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi shakhs jab subah karey aur jab Sham karey to sau baar (سبحان الله وبحمده) kahey to qiyamat ke roz koi shakhs us se behtar amal lekar nahi aayega , siwaey uske jo itni baar (ye kalimaat ( kahey ya us se zyada baar kahey ."
6844,"Abu-Ishaq ne Amr-bin-Memoon se riwayat ki, kaha : jis shakhs ne das baar :                                                                          (لا اله الا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله لحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير) padha wo us shakhs ki tarah hoga jisne Hazrat Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki nasl se char ghulam aazad kiye hon."
6845,"Shabi ne Rabe-bin-khushaim se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rabe se puchha : aap ne ye ( hadis) kis se sunii? unhon-ne kaha : Amr-bin-Memoon se, phir main Amr-bin-Memoon ke paas aaya, unse puchha : aap ne ye (hadis) kis se sunii? unhon-ne kaha : ibne-abi-Lela se, kaha : to main ibne-abi-Lela ke paas aaya aur unse puchha : aap ne ye (hadis) kis se sunii? unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se suni , wo usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kartey they."
6846,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do kalimey hain jo zaban par halkey hain aur meezaan mein bhari hain aur Allah ko bahut mahboob hain :                      (سبحان الله وبحمده سبحان اللہ العظيم ) Allah har us cheez se paak hai jo uske shaayaan shaan nahi aur sab hamd usi ke layaq hai, Allah har us cheez se paak hai jo uske shaayaane-shaan nahi aur azmat ki har sifat se bhara hai."
6847,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye baat ke main ( سبحان الله والحمدلله wla اله الا لله Allah ki qism اکبر) kahun , mujhey un tamam chizon se zyada mahboob hai jin par suraj tuloo hota hai."
6848,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ali-bin-Mus-hir aur ibne-Numair ne Musa Johni se hadis bayan ki, aur hamein Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne bhi yahi hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz unhi ke hain. padhi. unhon-ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Musa Johni ne Musab-bin-Sad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : mujhey kuchh kalimaat sikhaaiye jinhein main (bataur zikr) kaha karun. aap ne farmaya : ye kaha karo : (لا اله الا لله وحده لا شريك له اللہ اکبر كبيرا والحمدلله كثيرا وسبحان الله رب العالمين لا حول wla قوة الا بالله العزيز الحكيم) Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akela hai, uska koi Sharik nahi, Allah badaai mein sabse bada hai aur behad w hisab tareef Allah ki hai, Allah har us cheez se paak hai jo iske shaayane-shaan nahi, wo sarey jahaanon ka paalne wala hai, kisi mein burai se bachney ki taqat aur neki karne ki quwwat nahi magar sirf aur sirf Allah ki di hui jo sab par ghalib hai, badi hikmat wala hai. us shakhs ne kaha : ye kalimaat to mere rab ke liye hain, mere liye kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye kaho : ( اللهم اغفرلى وارحمنى واهدنى وارزقنى (aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh de, mujh par raham farma, mujhey hidayat de aur mujhey rizq ata farmaa. Musa ne kaha : jahan tak ( عافنى ( mujhey aafiyat ata kar ka talluq hai to iske barey mein mujhey thoda sa waham hai aur mujhey yaqin nahi hai, aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ne apni hadis mein Musa ka ye qaul naql nahi kya."
6849,"abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne kaha : hamein abu-Malik Ashjai ne apne walid (taariq bin Ashim Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : jo shakhs Islam qabool karta, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko un kalimaat ki taleem detey they : ( اللهم اغفرلى وارحمنى واهدنى وارزقنى ( Allah ! mujhey bakhsh de, mujh par raham farma, mujhey hidayat de aur mujhey rizq ata farma."
6850,"abu-Muawia ne kaha : hamein abu-Malik Ashjai ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, kaha : jab koi shakhs musalman hota to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko Namaz sikhatey, phir usko hukm detey ke un kalimaat ke sath dua kya karey : ( اللهم اغفرلى وارحمنى واهدنى وعافنى وارزقنى) ."
6851,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : abu-Malik ne hamein apne walid se khabar di ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, (is waqt) unke paas aik shakhs ne hazir ho kar kaha : Allah ke rasool! jab main apne rab se maangon to kya kaha karun? aap ne farmaya : tum kaho : ( اللهم اغفرلى وارحمنى واهدنى وعافنى وارزقنى) sath hi apne angoothey ke siwa (eik aik karke ( saari ungliyan band kartey gaey (aur farmaya : ( ye kalimaat tumharey liye tumhari duniya aur aakhirat donon jama kar dengey."
6852,"Musab bin Sad se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere walid (Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke aap ne farmaya : kya tum mein se koi shakhs is baat se aajiz hai ke har roz aik hazaar nekiyan kamaaey? aap ke sath baithey huey logon mein se aik ne puchha ham mein se koi shakhs aik hazaar nekiyan kis tarah kamaa sakta hai? aap ne farmaya : wo so baar subhanallah kahey. uske liye hazaar nekiyan likh di jaeyngi aur uske hazaar gunah mitaa diye jaengey."
6853,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne kisi musalman ki duniyawi takleefon mein se koi takleef door ki, Allah Taala uski qiyamat ki takleefon mein se koi takleef door karega. aur jis shakhs ne kisi tang dast ke liye aasani ki, Allah Taala uske liye duniya aur aakhirat mein aasani karega. aur jisne kisi musalman ki parda poshi ki, Allah Taala duniya aur aakhirat mein uski parda poshii karega. aur Allah Taala us waqt tak bandey ki madad mein laga rehta hai jab tak banda apne bhai ki madad mein laga rehta hai aur jo shakhs us rastey par chalta hai jis mein wo ilm hasil karna chahta hai to Allah Taala iske zariey se uske liye jannat ka rasta aasan kar deta hai. Allah ke gharon mein se kisi ghar mein logon ka koi giroh ikattha nahi hota, wo Quran ki tilawat kartey hain aur uska dars aur tadrees kartey hain magar un par sakeenat ( itminan aur sukoon qalb (ka nuzool hota hai aur) Allah ki) rehmat unko dhanp leti hai aur Farishtey unko apne gherey mein ley letey hain aur Allah Taala apne muqarrebeen (qareebon) mein jo uske paas hotey hain unka zikr karta hai aur jiske amal ne usey ( khair ke husool mein) peechhey rakha , uska nasb usey tez nahi kar sakta."
6854,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jis tarah abu-Muawia ki hadis hai, magar abu-Usama ki hadis mein tangdast ke liye aasani karne ka zikr nahi."
6855,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Abu-Ishaq ko abu-Muslim Aghrarr se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein gawahi deta hun, un donon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein gawahi di ke aap ne farmaya : jo qaum bhi izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ko yad karne ke liye baithti hai, unko Farishtey gher letey hain, rehmat dhanp leti hai aur un par itminan qalb nazil hota hai aur Allah unka zikr unmein karta hai jo uske paas hotey hain."
6856,"Abdur-Rehman ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6857,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) nikal kar masjid mein aik halqey ( walon (ke paas se guzrey , unhon-ne kaha : tumhen kis cheez ne yahan bitha rakha hai? unhon-ne kaha : ham Allah ka zikr karne ke liye baithey hain. unhon-ne kaha : kya Allah ko gawah bana kar kehtey ho ke tumhen iske ilawa aur kisi gharaz ne nahi bithaya? unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham iske alawa aur kisi wjah se nahi baithey, unhon-ne kaha : dekho , maine tum par kisi tohmat ki wjah se qism nahi di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney meri haisiyat ka koi shakhs aisa nahi jo hadis bayan karne mein mujh se kam ho, (iske bawajud apne yaqeeni ilm ki bina par main tumharey samney ye hadis bayan kar raha hun ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikal kar apne sathiyon ke aik halqey ke qareeb tashrif laey aur farmaya : tum kis gharaz se baithey ho? unhon-ne kaha : ham baithey Allah ka zikr kar rahe hain aur is baat par uski hamd kar rahe hain ke usne Islam ki taraf hamari rehnumai ki. iske zariey se ham par ehsan kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum Allah ko gawah bana kar kehtey ho ke tum sirf isi gharaz se baithey ho? unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham iske siwa aur kisi gharaz se nahi baithey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine tum par kisi tohmat ki wjah se tumhen qism nahi di, balke mere paas Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aaey aur mujhey bataya ke Allah Taala tumharey zariey se farishton ke samney fakhr ka izhar farma raha hai."
6858,"Sabit ne abu-Burda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat agral mazni (Raziallahu anhu) se, jinhein sharfe-sohbat hasil tha, riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere dil par ghubaar sa chhaa jata hai to main (is kaifiyat ke izaaley (khatmey) ke liye) aik din mein sau baar Allah se istighfar karta hun."
6859,"ghandar ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Umra-bin-murraa se aur unhon-ne abu-Burda se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aghrarr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. padhi. aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se they. wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey they, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logo ! Allah ki taraf tauba kiya karo kyonke main Allah se. aik din mein sau baar tauba karta hun."
6860,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz , Abu-Dawud aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Shoba se isi sanad se ( yahi ( riwayat ki."
6861,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne suraj ke maghrib se tuloo honey se pahley tauba kar li, Allah Taala uski tauba ko qabool farma lega ."
6862,"Muhammad-bin-Fuzail aur abu-Muawia ne Aasim se, unhon-ne abu-Usman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik safar mein ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke log buland awaz ke sath Allahu-akbar kehney lagey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey logo ! apni jaanon par narmi karo, tum na kisi behrey ko pukar rahe ho, na ghayab ko , tum usko pukar rahe ho jo har waqt khub sunney wala hai, qareeb hai aur tumharey sath hai. us waqt mein aap ke peechhey tha aur ye keh raha tha : (لا حول wla قوة الا بالله ) gunahon se bchney aur neki ki quwwat sirf aur sirf Allah se miltii hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abdullah-bin-Qais ! kya main tumhen jannat ke khazaanon mein se aik khazaaney ka pata na bataan? maine kaha : kyon nahi, Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : (لا حول wla قوة الا بالله ) kaha karo."
6863,Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Aasim se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
6864,"Yazeed bin Zure ne kaha : hamein (Sulaiman) Taimi ne abu-Usman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo log ( sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu)) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur wo aik ghaati par chadh rahe they, kaha : aik aadmi jab bhi oonchaai par chadhta zor se pukaarna shuru kar deta : (لا اله الا لله Allah ki qism اکبر) ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum log kisi behrey ko ya usey jo ghayab ho, nahi pukar rahe. kaha : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : abu-Musa ! ya ( farmaya : ( Abdullah-bin-Qais ! kya tumhen aisa kalima na bataaun jo jannat ke khazaaney mein se hai? maine arz ki, Allah ke rasool! wo kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (لا حول wla قوة الا بالله) (gunahon se bchney ki) koi koshish aur (neki karne ki) koi quwwat Allah ke siwa kisi se hasil nahi hoti."
6865,"Motamir ne apne walid (Sulaiman Taimi) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Usman ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah bayan kya."
6866,"Ayub ne abu-Usman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they, phir Aasim ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
6867,"Khalid Haza ne abu-Usman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham aik ghazwey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, phir us hadis ko bayan kya aur is mein kaha : (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( tum jisko pukar rahe ho wo tum mein se kisi ki ontni ki gardan ki nisbat bhi iske zyada qareeb hai. aur un ( Khalid Haza ( ki hadis main ( لا حول wla قوة الا بالله ) ka zikr nahi hai."
6868,"Usmaan-bin-Ghiyaas ne kaha : hamein abu-Usman ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah ne mujh se farmaya : kya main tumhen jannat ke khazaanon mein se aik kalima na bataaun? . padhi. ya farmaya : . padhi. jannat ke khazaanon mein se aik khazaaney ka pata na bataaun? maine kaha : kyon nahi (zaroor bataein) , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (لا حول wla قوة الا بالله )"
6869,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya : ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey aik dua sikhlaaiye jis ko main padha karun apni Namaz mein. Aap ne farmaya ye kaha kar ya Allah maine apne nafs par bada zulm kya hai ya bahut zulm kya hai aur gunahon ko koi nahi bakhshtaa siwa terey, to bakhsh de mujhey apne paas ki bakhshish se aur raham kar mujh par to bakhshney wala meharban hai."
6870,"Abdullah-bin Wahab ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein aik aadmi ne jiska unhon-ne naam liya aur Amr-bin-Haris ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se khabar di aur unhon-ne abul-Khair se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap mujhey aik aisi dua sikhaaiye jisko main apni Namaz mein bhi maanga karun aur apne ghar mein bhi maanga karun. padhi. phir Leis ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya. magar unhon-ne (baghair shak ke) (zulman kaseera) ( bahut zulm kya ( kaha,"
6871,"ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Allah Taala se) ye duaein maanga kartey they : aey Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun aag ke fitney se aur aag ke azab se aur ghina ki aazmaish ke shar se aur faqr ki aazmaish ke shar se aur main teri panah mein aata hun jhootey Masih ke fitney ki burai se. aey Allah! meri khataein barf aur olon (ke pani ( se dho de, aur mere dil ko khataaon se is tarah saaf suthra kar de jis tarah to safaid kapdey ko mail se saaf karta hai aur mere aur meri khataaon ke darmyan itna fasla daal de jitna fasla tu ney mashriq aur maghrib ke darmyan daala hai. aey Allah ! main susti, aajiz kar dene waley budhapey, gunah aur qarz (ke ghalbey) se teri panah mein aata hun."
6872,abu-Muawia aur Wakee ne hamein Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
6873,"ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman Taimi ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! main aajiz honey, susti, buzdili, budhapey aur kanjoosi se teri panah mein aata hun aur main qabr ke azab aur zindagi aur maut ki aazmaaishon se teri panah mein aata hun."
6874,"Yazeed bin Zure aur Motamir donon ne Taimi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta Yazeed ki hadis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qaul : aur zindagi aur maut ki aazmaaishon se (main teri panah mein aata hun) mazkoor nahi."
6875,"ibne-Mubarak ne Sulaiman Taimi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kai cheezon se, jinka unhon-ne zikr kya aur kanjoosi se Allah ki panah talab ki."
6876,"Shuaib bin Habhaab ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye duaein maanga kartey they : aey Allah! main kanjoosi, susti, zaleel tareen Umar, qabr ke azab aur zindagi aur maut ki aazmaaishon se teri panah mein aata hun."
6877,"Amr Naqid aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Sumai ne Abu-Saleh se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) insan ke haq mein bura Sabit hone-waale faisley , bad-bakhtii ke aa leney , apni takleef par dushmanon ke khush honey aur aajiz kar dene wali aazmaish se panah maanga kartey they. Amr ne apni hadis (ki sanad) mein kaha : Sufiyan ne kaha : mujhey shak hai ke) shayad ( maine un baton mein se koi aik baat badha di hai."
6878,"Leis ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se aur unhon-ne Haris bin Yaqoob se riwayat ki ke Yaqoob-bin-Abdullah ne unhein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed ko ye kehtey huey suna, maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, kaha : maine Hazrat Khaula binte- hakeem salmiya (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehti thin : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jo shakhs kisi ( bhi) manzil par utra aur us ne ye kalimaat kahey : main Allah (se us) ke mukammal tareen kalimaat ki panah talab karta hun har us cheez ke shar se jo usney paida ki, to us shakhs ko us manzil se chaley janey tak koi cheez nuqsan nahi pahunchaaeygi."
6879,"Abdullah-bin Wahab ne kaha : hamein Amr-bin-Haris ne khabar di ke Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib aur Haaris-bin-Yaqoob ne unhein Yaqoob bin-Abdullah-bin-ashajj se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Khaula binte- hakeem salmiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : tum mein se koi shakhs jab kisi manzil par pahunchey to ye kalimaat kahey : main har us cheez ke shar se jo Allah ne paida ki, uske mukammal tareen kalimaat ki panah mein aata hun, is tarah wahan se kooch kar janey tak koi bhi cheez usey nuqsan nahi pahunchaaeygi."
6880,"Yaqoob ne kaha : qaqa-bin-Hakim ne Zakwan se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : aik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! mujhey us bichhu se kitni shadeed takleef pahunchi jisne kal raat mujhey kaat liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tumne jab raat ki thi, ye (kalimaat) keh detey : main har us cheez ke shar se jisey Allah ne paida kya, iske kaamil tareen kalimaat ki panah mein aata hun to wo ( bichhu) tumhen koi nuqsan na pahunchata ."
6881,"Leis ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se, unhon-ne Jafar se, unhon-ne Yaqoob se riwayat ki, unhon-ne unko bataya ke Ghatfan ke aazad karda ghulam Abu-Saleh ne unhein bataya, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! mujhey bichhu ne kaat liya. (aagey) ibne-Wahab ki hadis ki tarah hai."
6882,"Mansoor ne Sad bin Ubeda se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum apne bistar par janey lago to apni Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah wuzu karo, phir apni daain karwat leto , phir ye kaho : aey Allah! maine apna chehra terey sipurd kar diya aur apna mamla terey hawale kar diya aur apni kamar terey sahaarey par tika di, ye sab tujh se ummeed aur terey khof ke sath kya. terey siwa tujh se na kahin panah mil sakti hai, na nijat hasil ho sakti hai. main teri kitab par eman laya jo tuney nazil ki aur terey Nabi par eman laya jisey tuney maboos kya. un kalimaat ko tum (apni zaban se ada hone-waale) aakhiri kalimaat bana lo (unke baad aur kuchh na bolo) to us raat agar tumhen maut aa gaee to fitrat par maut aaeygii. (hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine un kalimaat ko yad karne ke liye unhein dohraya to kaha : main terey rasool par eman laya jisey tuney bheja to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( yun ( kaho : main terey Nabi par eman laya jisey tuney bhejaa."
6883,"Husain ne Sad bin Ubeda se, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis riwayat ki, magar Mansoor ne zyada mukammal hadis bayan ki aur Husain ki hadis mein ye izafa kya : agar ye ( kehney wala ( subah karega to khair hasil karega ."
6884,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne Abu-Dawud se aur ibne-Bashar ne Abdur-Rehman aur Abu-Dawud donon se riwayat ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Sad-bin-Ubaida se suna, wo Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko hukm diya ke jab wo raat ko apni khuwab gaah mein janey lagey to ( dua kartey huey) ye kahey : aey Allah ! maine apni jaan terey sipurd kar di aur apna chehra teri taraf mutwajjeh kar liya aur apni kamar terey sahaarey par tika di aur apna mamla terey hawale kar diya, ye sab tujhi se ummeed kartey huey aur tujhi se dartey huey kya. tujh se khud terey siwa na panah ki koi jagah hai na nijat ki. main teri kitab par eman laya jo tuney nazil ki aur terey rasool par eman laya jisey tuney bheja, phir agar (is raat) usey maut aa gaee to fitrat par maut aaeygi. ibne-Bashar ne apni hadis mein : raat ke waqt (bistar par janey lagey) ke alfaz nahi kahey."
6885,"abu-Ahwas ne Abu-Ishaq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs se farmaya : aey falan! jab tum apne bistar par letney lago. iske baad Amr-bin-Murra ki hadis ki tarah hai. ( magar abu-Ahwas ne Mansoor ki riwayat ki tarah) ye alfaz kahey : (aur mein eman laya) terey Nabi par jisey tuney bheja, phir agar tum us raat mar gaey to (theek) fitrat par marogey aur agar tum ne ( zinda haalat mein) subah kar li to khair ( w bhalai ( hasil karogey."
6886,"Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko hukm diya, usi ki tarah , aur unhon-ne agar tum ne ( zinda haalat mein) subah ki to khair hasil karogey ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
6887,Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bistar par tashrif ley jatey to ye dua kartey : aey Allah! main terey naam se jeeta hun aur terey naam se wafat paaunga aur jab bedaar hotey to farmatey : Allah ki hamd hai jisne hamein wafat dene ke baad zinda kar diya aur usi ki taraf (qiyamat ke roz) zinda ho kar jana hai.
6888,"Aqba bin Mukarram aur Abu-Bakar bin Naafe ne kaha : hamein ghandar ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Khalid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Haaris ko Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey suna, unhon-ne aik shakhs se kaha ke jab wo apne bistar par jaey to ye dua karey : aey Allah ! meri jaan ko tuney paida kya aur tu hi usko maut dega, us jaan ki maut bhi aur zindagi bhi terey hi liye hai, agar to usko zinda rakhey to uski hifazat farmana aur agar to usko maut de to uski maghfirat karna, aey Allah ! main tujh se aafiyat mangta hun. aik shakhs ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap ne ye hadis Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suni hai? unhon-ne kaha : unse jo Hazrat umr se zyada afzal hain (maine ye hadis) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (suni hai.) ibne-Naafe ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Abdullah-bin-Haaris se riwayat hai, ye nahi kaha : maine suna."
6889,"Jarir ne Suhel se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : (mere walid) Abu-Saleh hamein hukm diya kartey they ke jab ham mein se koi shakhs soney ka irada karey to bistar par daain karwat letey, phir dua karey : aey Allah! aey aasmanon ke rab aur zamin ke rab aur arsh aur farsh ke rab, aey hamarey rab aur har cheez ke rab , daney aur guthliyon ko cheer ( kar paudey aur darakht ugaa ( dene waley ! Taurait , Injeel aur furqan ko nazil karne waley ! main har us cheez ke shar se teri panah mein aata hun jiski peshani terey qabzey mein hai, aey Allah! tu hi awwal hai, tujh se pahley koi cheez nahi, aey Allah! tu hi aakhir hai, terey baad koi cheez nahi hai, tu hi zahir hai, terey uper koi cheez nahi hai, tu hi baatin hai, tujh se peechhey koi cheez nahi hai, hamari taraf se (hamara) qarz ada kar aur hamein faqr se ghina ata farmaa. wo us hadis ko Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo ( aagey ( usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey they."
6890,"Khalid Tahan ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein ye hukm diya kartey they ke jab ham apne bistaron par letein to ye dua karein, Jarir ki hadis ki tarah (aur Khalid Tahan ne har us cheez ke shar se ke bajaey) kaha : har us jaandaar ke shar se (teri panah chahta hun) jisey tuney uski peshani se pakda hua hai."
6891,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik khaadim maangney ke liye aain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (jawab mein) unse kaha : (beti!) tum kaha karo : aey Allah ! saaton aasmanon ke rab! jis tarah Suhel ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se riwayat ki."
6892,"Anas bin ayaaz ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed bin abi Saeed Maqbari ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs apne bistar par letna chahey to apne tehband ka androoni hissey lekar us se apne bistar ko jhaadey, phir bismillaah kahey kyonke wo nahi janta ke us (ke uth janey) ke baad iske bistar par (makhlooqat mein se) kon aaya? phir jab letnaa chahey to apni daain karwat letey aur kahey : mere parwardigar ! to (har na-shaayaan baat se) paak hai, maine terey ( hukm ( se apna pahlu ( bistar par) rakha aur terey hi hukm se usey uthaaunga agar tu ney meri Rooh ko (apne paas) rok liya to uski maghfirat kar dena aur agar tuney usey ( wapas ( bhej diya to uski isi tarah hifazat farmana jis tarah to apne nek bandon ki hifazat farmata hai."
6893,"Abda ne Ubaidullah-bin-Umar se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis riwayat ki aur kaha : phir wo ye hai : terey naam se aey parwardigar ! maine apna pahlu tikaaya , agar tuney meri jaan ko zinda kya to is par rehmat farmana."
6894,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bistar par jatey to farmatey : Allah Taala ki hamd hai jisne hamein khilaaya, pilaya, (har tarah se) kafi hua aur hamein thikana diya. kitney log hain jinka na koi kifaayat karne wala hai na thikana dene wala."
6895,"Mansoor ne Hilal se aur unhon-ne farwa bin Nofal Ashjai se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah Taala se kya duaein kya kartey they? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua kya kartey they : aey Allah ! jo maine kya uske shar se aur jo maine nahi kya, uske shar se teri panah mein aata hun."
6896,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Husain se, unhon-ne Hilal se aur unhon-ne farwa bin Nofal se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya dua farmaya kartey they? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aap ye dua farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! maine jo kaam kiye hain, unke shar se aur jo kaam maine nahi kiye, unke shar se teri panah chahta hun."
6897,"ibne-abi Adi aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar donon ne Shoba se aur unhon-ne Husain se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar Muhammad-bin-Jafar ki hadis main ( وشر ما لم ( aamal ke bajaey) (و من شر ما لم اعمل) hai."
6898,"Abda bin abu-Lubaba ne Hilaal-bin-Yasaaf se, unhon-ne Farwa bin Nofal se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni dua mein farmatey they : aey Allah ! main un kaamon ke shar se jo maine kiye aur unke shar se jo nahi kiye, teri panah mein aata hun."
6899,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (dua kartey huey) farmaya kartey they : aey Allah! main terey liye farmaanbardaar ho gaya, terey sath eman laya, tujh par bharosa kya, teri taraf ruju kya aur teri madad se (kufr ke saath) mukhaasimat ki. aey Allah! main is baat se teri izzat ki panah leta hun. padhi. terey siwa koi maabood nahi. padhi. ke to mujhey seedhi raah se hata de. padhi. tu hi hamesha zinda rehney wala hai jis ko maut nahi aa sakti aur jin w insan sab mar jaengey."
6900,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi safar mein hotey aur sahar ke waqt uthtey to farmatey : ( hamari taraf se) Allah ki hamd aur uske inaam ki khoobsoorti (ke aetraaf) ka sunney wala ye baat dusron ko bhi suna de. aey hamarey rab! hamarey sath reh, ham par ehsan kar, main aag se Allah ki panah maangtey huey ye dua kar raha hun."
6901,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Barda bin abu-Musa Ash-ari se, unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ye dua farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! meri khata meri la ilmi , apne ( kisi) mamley mein mera had se aagey ya peechhey reh jana aur wo sab kuchh jo meri nisbat to zyada janta hai sab maaf farma de. aey Allah ! mere wo sab kaam jo ( tujhey pasand na aaey hon ( maine sanjeedagi se kiye hon ya mazaahan kiye hon, bhool chook kar kiye hon ya jaan-bojh kar kiye hon aur ye sab mujh se huey hon, unko bakhsh de. aey Allah ! meri wo baatein (jo tujhey pasand nahi aaein ( bakhsh de jo maine pahley kiin ya jo maine baad mein kin, akeley mein kin ya jo maine sab ke samney kin aur jinhein to mujh se zyada jaanney wala hai, tu hi (jisey chahey apni rehmat ki taraf) aagey badhaney wala hai aur tu hi peechhey karne wala hai aur to har cheez par qaadir hai."
6902,Abdul-Malik bin Sabaah Mismai ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad se ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
6903,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! mere Deen ko durust kar de, jo mere ( Deen w duniya ke) har kaam ke tahaffuz ka zaria hai aur meri duniya ko durust kar de jis mein meri guzraan hai aur meri aakhirat ko durust kar de jis mein mera (apni manzil ki taraf ( lautna hai aur meri zindagi ko mere liye har bhalai mein izaafey ka sabab bana de aur meri wafat ko mere liye har shar se raahat bana de."
6904,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin Bishr ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Ahwas se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! main tujh se hidayat , taqwa , paak daamani, aur (dil ka ( ghinaa mangta hun."
6905,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Ishaq se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta ibne-Musanna ne apni riwayat main ((afaaf ( ki bajaey) iffat ka lafz kaha, (mafhoom aik hi hai.)"
6906,"Abdullah-bin-Haaris aur abu-Usmaan nehdi ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main tumhen isi tarah bataataa hun jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha, aap farmatey they : aey Allah ! main tujh se teri panah mein aata hun, aajiz ho janey , sustii , buzdili, kanjoosi, sakht budhapey aur qabr ke azab se. aey Allah ! mere dil ko taqwa de, usko pakeeza kar de, tu hi us (dil) ko sabse behtar paak karne wala hai, tu hi iska rakhwaalaa aur iska madadgaar hai. aey Allah ! main tujh se aisey ilm se teri panah mangta hun jo koi fayda na de aur aisey dil se jo (terey aagey) jhuk kar mutmain na hota ho aur aisey man se jo sair na ho aur aisi dua se jisey sharfe-qabooliyat naseeb na ho."
6907,"abdul-Wahid-bin-Ziyad ne Hasan-bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ibrahim-bin-Sad Nakhai ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Sham hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua kartey they : ham ne Sham ki aur Sara mulk (Sham ke waqt bhi) Allah ka hua, sab shukr aur tareef Allah ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa ( Malik , maabood ( hai, uska koi Sharik nahi. Hasan (bin-Ubaidullah) ne kaha : mujhey Zaid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne is (dua) mein (ye hissey ( Ibrahim ( Nakhai ( se ( sun kar) hifz kiya : usi ki baadshaahi aur usi ke liye har tarah ki tareef hai aur wo har cheez par poori tarah qaadir hai. aey Allah ! main tujh se us raat ki bhalai mangta hun aur tujh se us raat ki aur uske baad (ke har lamhey ( ki burai se panah talab karta hun, aey Allah ! main kasl mandi (sustee) aur budhapey ki kharabi se teri panah mein aata hon, aey Allah ! main teri panah mangta hun jahannam mein kisi bhi qism ke azab se aur qabr mein kisi bhi qism ke azab se."
6908,"Jarir ne Hasan-bin-Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Ibrahim-bin-Suwed se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Sham kartey to (dua kartey huey) farmatey : ham aur Sara mulk Sham ke waqt bhi Allah ka hua, sab hamd Allah ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa hai, uska koi Sharik nahi. (Hasan-bin-Ubaidullah ne) kaha : main dekhta hun ke unhon (Ibrahim Nakhai) ne un kalimaat mein ye bhi kaha : saari badhshahat usi ki hai, (har nemat par) saari tareef bhi usi ke qaabil hai, wahi har cheez par poori qudrat rakhney wala hai. aey mere parwardigar ! jo kuchh s raat mein hai aur jo iske baad hai, main tujh se uski bhalai ka talabgaar hun aur jo kuchh is raat mein hai aur jo iske baad hai uski burai se main teri panah mein aata hun. aey mere parwardigar ! main teri panah chahta hun kasl mandi (sustee) se aur budhapey ki kharabi se. aey mere parwardigar ! main tujh se panah mangta hun jahannam mein kisi bhi qism ke azab se aur qabr mein kisi bhi qism ke azab se. aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah kartey to (bilkul usi tarah) farmatey : ham aur saari badhshahat aur ikhtiyar subah ko (bhi) Allah ke huey."
6909,"Zayda ne Hasan-bin-Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Ibrahim-bin-Suwaid se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sham ke waqt ( dua kartey huey ye ( farmaya kartey they : ham ne aur sarey mulk ne Allah ke) hukm aur farman ki pabandi ke) liye Sham ki. sab tareef Allah ke liye hai, Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa hai, uska koi Sharik nahi. aey Allah ! main tujh se is raat ki aur is mein maujood har bhalai ka sawal karta hun aur main tujh se is raat ke aur is mein maujood har shar se panah ka talabgaar hun. aey Allah ! main teri panah mangta hun, susti taari ho janey se aur umr (ke had se) badh janey se aur budhapey ki kharabi se aur duniya ke har fitney aur qabr ke azab se. Hasan-bin- Ubaidullah ne kaha : Zubeda ne mujhey Ibrahim-bin Suwaid ( Nakhai ( se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey huey mazeed ye bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (jab Sham kartey to) ye farmatey : Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa hai, uska koi Sharik nahi, saari badhshahat usi ki hai, sab tareef usi ke qaabil hai aur wahi har cheez par qaadir hai."
6910,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (dua kartey huey ye) farmaya kartey they : akeley Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, us ne apne lashkar ko izzat di, apne bandey ki nusrat ki, akelaa wo tamam jamaton par ghalib aaya,  (wahi aakhir hai) uske baad kuchh nahi."
6911,"abu-Kuraib Muhammad-bin-Alaa ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein ( Abdullah ( bin-Idrees ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Aasim-bin-kaleeb se suna, unhon-ne abu-Barda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : (dua kartey huey ye) kaho : aey Allah ! mujhey hidayat de aur mujhey seedhey rastey par chala , aur (aey Ali !) hidayat (ka naam letey huey us) se sahi rastey par chalney ko zahan mein rakho aur seedha rehney se teer jaisi sadhaai murad lo (maangtey huey hidayat aur sawab ka kamaal talab karo.)"
6912,"ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Idris ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aasim-bin-kaleeb ne isi sanad ke sath khabar di (ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : (aey Ali ! ye ( kaho : aey Allah ! main tujh se hidayat aur raasti ka sawal karta hun. phir usi ki tarah bayan kiya."
6913,"Kureb ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padhney ke baad subah sawerey unke yahaan se bahar tashrif le gaey, is waqt wo apni Namaz padhney wali jagah mein thin, phir din chadhney ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas wapas tashrif laey to wo (usi tarah) baithi hui thin. aap ne farmaya : tum ab tak usi haalat mein baithi hui ho jis par main tumhen chhod kar gaya tha? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey (yahaan se janey ke) baad maine char kalimey teen baar kahey hain, agar unko inke sath tolaa jaey jo tum ne aaj ke din ab tak kaha hai to ye unse wazan mein badh jayen :                                                                        (سبحان الله وبحمده عدد خلقہ ورضا نفسہ وزنۃ عرشۃ ومداد كلماتہ)                                                                                                         ''pakeezgi hai Allah ki aur uski tareef ke sath , jitni uski makhlooq ki ginti hai aur jitni usko pasand hai aur jitna uske arsh ka wazan aur jitni uske kalimaat ki siyaahi hai.''"
6914,"abu-Rushdain ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : subah ki Namaz ke waqt ya subah ki Namaz ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) guzartey huey unke yahaan tashrif laey. padhi. phir us (pichhli hadis) ke mutabiq bayan kiya. padhi. magar unhon-ne (apne kalimon ko is tarah) bayan kiya : main Allah ki tasbeeh bayan karta hun jitni uski makhlooqat ki gintii hai, main Allah ki tasbeeh bayan karta hun jitni uski raza hai, main Allah ki tasbeeh bayan karta hun jitna uske arsh ka wazan hai, main Allah ki tasbeeh karta hun jitni uske kalimaat ki siyaahi hai."
6915,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine ibne-abi-Lela se suna, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko chakki peesney se jo zahmat bardasht karni padi uski wjah se unke hathon mein takleef hui. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh qaidi aaey. aap ki taraf gain, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) ghar mein) na paya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se milin aur unhein (apni takleef ke barey mein) bataya. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aapko un (hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) (ke apne paas aaney ke barey mein bataya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey yahaan tashrif laey. padhi. us waqt ham apne apney bistaron mein ja chukey they. ham khadey honey lagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : donon apni apni jagah par raho. aap ham donon ke darmyan ( wali jagah par) baith gaey yahan tak ke maine aap ke qadam Mubarak ki thandak apne seeney par mehsus ki, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum donon ne jo mujh se maanga hai main tumhen us se behtar baat na sikhlaaoon? jab tum donon apne apney bistaron mein jao to chauntis (34) baar Allahu-akbar kaho, tentis (33) baar Subhan-Allah kaho aur tentis (33) baar Alhamdulilah kaho , ye (amal ( tum donon ke liye aik khaadim (mil janey) se behtar hai."
6916,"Wakee, Muaz aur ibne-abi-Adi sab ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur Muaz ki hadis mein hai : jab tum donon raat ke waqt apne bistar mein chaley jao."
6917,"Ubaidullah-bin-abi-Yazeed aur Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne ibne-abi-Lela se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah Hakam ne ibne-abi-Lela se riwayat ki. unhon-ne hadis mein mazeed ye bayan kiya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat suni maine kabhi usey tark nahi kiya. unse puchha kya : jange-siffeen ki raat bhi nahi chhoda? unhon-ne jawab diya :  jange-siffeen ki raat bhi) usey nahi chhoda ). Ata ne jo hadis Mujahid se aur unhon-ne ibne-abi-Lela se riwayat ki, unhon ( ibne-abi-Lela ( ne kaha : maine un (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha :  jange-siffeen ki raat bhi na chhoda?"
6918,"Rooh-bin-Qasim ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid (Abu-Saleh) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aik khidmat guzaar (kaneez) maangney ke liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein aur aap se kaam ki shikayat ki to aap ne farmaya : tumhen khidmat guzaar to hamarey yahaan nahi mila. (hamarey ghar mein bhi maujood nahi), farmaya : kya main tumhen aisi baat na bataaun jo tumharey liye khidmat guzaar se bahut behtar hai? jab tum bistar par jao to tentis (33) baar Subhan-Allah kaho, tentis (33) baar الحمدللہ (Alhamdulillah) kaho aur chauntis (34) baar Allahu-akbar kaho."
6919,Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Suhel ne isi sanad ke sath (yahi) hadis bayan ki.
6920,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum murgh ki aawaz suno to Allah Taala se uske Fazal ka sawal karo, kyonke (us waqt) us ne aik Farishtey ko dekha hai aur jab tum gadhey ki aawaz suno to shaitan se Allah ki panah maango kyonke us ne shaitan ko dekha hai."
6921,"Muaz-bin-Hisham ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Aaliya se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bechaini ke waqt ye dua kiya kartey they : Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi jo sabse azeem hai, sabse zyada hilm wala hai. Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi jo arshe-azeem ka Malik hai. Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi jo aasmanon ka Malik , zaminon ka Malik aur izzat waley arsh ka Malik hai."
6922,"Wakee ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, lekin Muaz-bin-Hisham ki hadis zyada mukammal hai."
6923,"hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se riwayat ki, abu-Aaliya riyaahi ne unhein Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bechaini ke waqt in alfaz se dua farmatey they, phir wahi kalimaat zikr kiye jo Muaz-bin-Hisham ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Qatada se riwayat kiye, magar unhon-ne   ((رب السماوات و رب الارض) ke bajaey) (رب السماوات والارض) kaha,"
6924,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne kaha : mujhey Yousuf-bin-Abdullah-bin-Haaris ne abu-Aaliya se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab koi sakht mushkil aur takleef deh mamla darpesh hota to aap farmatey, phir isi tarah bayan kiya jis tarah Muaz ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki hai aur un kalimaat ke sath (لا الہ الا لله العظيم الحليم) ke baad (لا الہ الا لله رب العرش الكريم) mazeed bayan kiya."
6925,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Saeed Jurairi ne abu Abdullah jasri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne-Samit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya gaya : (Allah ke zikr ke liye) kon sa kalima afzal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisey Allah ne apne farishton ke liye ya (un samet ( apne tamam bandon ke liye muntakhab farmaya hai : (سبحان الله وبحمده) main (har nemat ke liye) Allah ki hamd ke sath har na-shaayaan cheez se uski pakeezgi bayan karta hun."
6926,"Shoba ne Jarir se, unhon-ne abu-Adbullah jasri se jo anza qabeeley se they, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Samit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen wo kalima na bataaun jo Allah Taala ko sabse zyada mahboob hai? maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! mujhey wo kalima bataiye jo Allah Taala ko sabse zyada mahboob hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ko sabse zyada mahboob kalima (سبحان الله وبحمده) hai."
6927,"Fuzel ne Talha bin Ubaidullah bin kurez se, unhon-ne Umme- Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi musalman banda nahi jo apne bhai ki peeth peechhey uske liye dua karey, magar aik farishta (hai jo ( kehta hai : tumhen bhi iske jaisi miley."
6928,"Musa bin Sarwaan Muallim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Talha bin Ubaidullah bin kurez ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Umme- Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mere aaqa ( khawind ( ne mujh se bayan kya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jis shakhs ne apne bhai ke liye uski peeth peechhey dua ki to jo farishta uske sath muqarrar hai wo kehta hai : Aameen aur tumhen bhi usi ki tarah ata ho."
6929,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Malik bin abi Sulaiman ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Safwan ke betey Safwan se riwayat ki, (hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti) Darda, un (safwaan) ki zaujiyat mein thi, wo kehtey hain : aur main Sham (Syria) aaya to Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan unke ghar gaya, wo nahi miley, main Hazrat umme-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum is saal Haj ka irada rakhtey ho? maine kaha : ji haan. unhon-ne kaha : hamarey liye khair ki dua karna kyonke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : musalman ki apne bhai ke liye uski peeth peechhey ki gaee dua mustajaab hoti hai, uske sar ke qareeb aik farishta muqarrar hota hai, wo jab bhi apne bhai ke liye duaae-khair karta hai to muqarrar kya hua farishta is par kehta hai : aameen, aur tumhen bhi usi ki tarah ata ho."
6930,"Safwan ne kaha : main bazar ki taraf nikla to Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi meri mulaqat hui, unhon-ne bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey huey mujh se wahi kuchh kaha (jo unki biwi Hazrat umme-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha.)"
6931,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne Abdul-Malik bin abi Sulaiman se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur kaha : Safwan bin-Abdullah-bin Safwan se riwayat hai,"
6932,"abu-Usama aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne Zakariya-bin abi Zayda se, unhon-ne Saeed bin abi Burda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala is baat par (apne ( bandey se razi hota hai ke wo aik khana khaaey aur is par Allah ki hamd karey ya peeney ki koi cheez (pani, doodh wghaira) piye aur is par Allah ki hamd kare."
6933,"Ishaq bin-Yoosuf azraq ne kaha : hamein Zakariya-bin abi Zayda ne Saeed bin abi Burda se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ( aagey ( usi ki tarah ( hai.)"
6934,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne ibne- azhar ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Ubaid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi shakhs ki dua us waqt tak qabool hoti hai jab tak wo jald bazi kartey huey ye nahi kehta : maine dua ki, lekin mere haq mein qabool nahi hoti . padhi. ya nahi hui."
6935,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Ubaid ne hadis bayan ki. padhi. aur wo Qurra (behtreen andaz mein Quran padhnewalon) aur ahale-fiqh (Islami Qanunon ke expert) mein se hain. padhi. unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi bhi shakhs ki dua qabool hoti hai jab tak wo jald bazi na karey aur ye ( na ( kahey : maine apne rab se dua ki to usne mujhey meri dua ka jawab nahi diya ( meri dua qabool nahi ki.)"
6936,"abu-Idrees Kholani ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jab tak koi banda gunah ya qata rehmi ki dua na karey aur qabooliyat ke mamley mein jald bazi na karey, uski dua qabool hoti rehti hai. kaha gaya : Allah ke rasool! jald bazi karna kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo kahey : maine dua ki aur maine dua ki aur mujhey nazar nahi aata ke wo mere haq mein qabool karega, phir us marhaley mein (maayus ho kar) thak jaey aur dua karna chhod de."
6937,"Hammaad-bin-Salma , Muaaz-bin-Muaaz Anbari , Motamir , Jarir aur Yazeed bin Zure ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman Taimi ne abu-Usman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main jannat ke darwazey par khada hua to zyada tar log jo usmein dakhil huey, miskeen they aur maine dekha ke maal w mataa waley (jannati) bahar rokey huey they, siwaey ( maaldaar ( dozkhiyon ke , unhein jahannam mein dalney ka hukm ( fauran hi ( saadir kar diya gaya tha aur main jahannam ke darwazey par khada hua to dekha ke usmein dakhil honey wali beshtar auratein thin."
6938,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne Ayub se, unhon-ne abu-Rijaa Utaridi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine jannat ke andar jhank kar dekha to maine ahle-jannat mein aksariyat fuqara ki dekhi aur maine dozakh mein jhank kar dekha to maine dozakh mein aksariyat aurton ki dekhi."
6939,Abdul-Wahab) Saqafi ne bataya : Ayub ne hamein isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
6940,"abu-Ash-hab ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu -Rijaa ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aag (jahannam) mein jhank kar dekha. phir Ayub ki hadis ki tarah zikr kya."
6941,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne abu-Rijaa se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, phir usi ki tarah zikr kya."
6942,"Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Tayyah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Mutarrif bin-Abdullah ki 2 beeviyan thin, wo aik biwi ke paas se aaey to dusri ne kaha : tum falan aurat (doosri biwi ka naam liya (ke paas se aaey ho? unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se ( bhi ho kar) aaya hun aur unhon-ne hamein ye hadis bayan ki hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat mein rehney walon mein sabse kam tadaad aurton ki hai."
6943,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Tayyah se hadis sunai, kaha : maine Mutarrif ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke unki 2 beeviyan thin ( aagey ( Muaz ki hadis ke ham mana (riwaayat ki.)"
6944,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki duaon mein se aik ye thi : aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun teri nemat ke zawaal se, teri aafiyat ke hat janey se, teri naa-gahaani saza se aur teri har tarah ki naaraazagi se."
6945,"Saeed bin Mansoor ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan aur Motamir bin Sulaiman ne Sulaiman Taimi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Usman nehdi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine apne baad koi aazmaish nahi chhodi jo mardon ke liye aurton (ki aazmaish) se badh kar nuqsan pahunchaney wali ho."
6946,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz Anbari, Suwed-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala ne hamein Motamir se hadis bayan ki. ibne- Muaz ne kaha : hamein Motamir bin Sulaiman ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne kaha : hamein abu-Usman ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid aur Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, un donon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main apne baad logon mein koi aisa fitna chhod kar nahi ja raha jo mardon ke liye aurton se badh kar nuqsan pahunchane-wala ho."
6947,"abu-Khalid Ahmar, Hushaim aur Jarir sab ne Sulaiman Taimi se, isi sanad ke sath, usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6948,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin-Bashar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Salma se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Nazara se suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah duniya bahut meethi aur hari-bhari hai aur Allah Taala usmein tumhen (tum se pahley walon ka ( ja-nashin banaaney wala hai, phir wo dekhega ke tum kaisey amal kartey ho, lihaza tum duniya (mein kho janey se) bachtey rehna aur aurton (ke fitney mein mubtala honey) se bach kar rehna, isliye ke Bani-Israeel mein sabse pehla fitna aurton (ke mamley) mein tha aur Bishr ki hadis mein hai : taake wo dekhey ke tum kis tarah amal kartey ho."
6949,"Anas bin ayaaz abu zamra ne Musa-bin-Aqba se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. aap ne farmaya : teen aadmi paidal chaley ja rahe they ke unhein barish ne aa liya, unhon-ne pahaad mein aik ghaar ki panah li, to ( achcha ( unke ghaar ke munh par pahaad se aik chattaan aa giri aur unke uper aa kar unhein dhaank diya, unhon-ne aik doosrey se kaha : tum apne un nek aamaal par nazar dalo jo tum ne ( sirf aur sirf ( Allah ke liye kiye hon aur unke waseeley se Allah Taala se dua karo, shayad wo us bandish aur qaid se tumhen aazad kar de. is par unmein se aik ne kaha, aey Allah ! mere intihai boodhey waalidain , biwi aur chhotey chhotey bachchey hain jinki main nigehdaasht karta hun. jab Sham ko main apne janwar (charaney ke baad unhein) unke paas wapas laata, unka doodh dohta to shuruat apne waalidain se karta aur apne bachchon se pahley unhein pilaata tha. aik din (maweshiyon ke charney ke qaabil ( darakhton ki talash mujhey bahut door ley gaee, mein raat se pahley ghar na pahunch saka. maine unhein paya ke wo donon so chukey hain. main jis tarah (har roz) doodh nikala karta tha nikala aur wo doha hua doodh lekar unke sarhaaney khada ho gaya. mujhey ye bhi na-pasand tha ke unko neend se jagaaoon aur ye bhi gawara na tha ke unse pahley bachchon ko pilaaun, bachchey bhook ki shiddat se bilaktey huey mere qadmon mein lot-pot ho rahe they, main usi haal main (khada) raha aur wo bhi usi haalat mein rahe yahan tak ke subah tuloo ho gaee. (aey Allah!) agar to janta hai ke maine ye sirf teri raza ke liye kya hai to us ( ghaar ke band munh ( mein itna suraakh kar de ke ham aasman ko dekh lein. Allah ne usmein aik suraakh kar diya ke wo aasman ko dekhney lagey aur doosra ( sathi ( kehney laga : aey Allah ! meri aik chacha zaad thi, main us se wahi shadeed mohabbat karta tha jo aik mard aurat se karta hai. maine us se apne liye ( khud ( usi ko maanga . us ne us waqt tak (meri baat manney se) inkar kar diya, yahan tak ke main usey ( soney ke) so Dinar la kar dun. main unhein hasil karne mein lag gaya yahan tak ke so Dinar ikatthey kar liye, phir jab main iske donon qadmon ke darmyan pahuncha to wo kehney lagi : Allah ke bandey ! Allah se dar aur haq ( nikah (ke baghair mehar (bikaarat) na tod. to ( tera naam sun kar) main us se ( alag ho kar) khada ho gaya. agar to janta hai ke maine ye tujhey razi karne ke liye kya tha to usmein (aur zyada) suraakh kar de ( Allah ne) unke liye (aur zyada ( suraakh kar diya aur teesrey ne ( dua kartey huey) kaha : aey Allah ! maine aik mazdoor ko chaawlon ke aik farq ( teen saa , taqriban saadhey saat (7) Kg ( ki ujrat ke iwaz kaam par lagaya. jab us ne apna kaam pura kar liya to kaha : mera haq ( ujrat ( ada karo. maine usey iska farq ( teen saa chaawal ( pesh kya. wo ( usey kam qarar detey huey) usko chhod kar chala gaya. main musalsal us ( teen saa chaawlon) ko kaasht karne laga, yahan tak ke maine us (ki aamadni) se gaaey (ke bahut se rewad) aur unko charaney waley ( ghulam ( ikatthey kar liye. phir (muddat baad) wo mere paas ( wapas ( aaya aur kaha : Allah se daro, mere haq mein mujh par zulm na karo. maine kaha : un gaayon (ke rewadon (aur unhein charaney waley ( ghulaamon ( ki taraf jao aur unhein ley lo. usne kaha : Allah se daro ! mere sath mazaaq to na karo. maine kaha : main mazaaq nahi kar raha, ye sab gaaein aur unko charaney waley ( ghulam ( ley jao, wo unhein lekar chala gaya. agar to janta hai ke maine ye sirf tujhey razi karne ke liye kya tha to jo hissey baqi reh gaya hai, usey bhi khol de. Allah ne baqi hissey bhi khol diya (aur wo aazad ho kar ghaar se bahar nikal aaey.)"
6950,"Musa-bin-Aqba, Ubaidullah, Fuzail, raqba bin masqala aur Saleh bin kaisaan sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se abu-Zamra ki Musa-bin-Aqba se riwayat ki hui hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki aur unhon-ne unki hadis main (paidal chaley ja rahe they ke saath) aur wo paidal chaltey huey nikley ke alfaz badhaatey aur Ubaidullah ki riwayat ko chhod kar Saleh ki hadis mein wo mil kar paidal chaley ke alfaz hain jabke un ( Ubaidullah ( ki hadis main aur wo nikley ka lafz hai aur unhon-ne iske baad) paidal chaltey huey wghaira) ka kuchh zikr nahi kya."
6951,"Salim bin-Abdullah (bin umr ( ne mujhey khabar di ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : tum se pahley logon mein se teen shakhs (kisi gharaz se) rawaana huey, yahan tak ke raat guzarney ki zarurat unhein aik ghaar ki panah-gaah mein ley aai phir unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Naafe ki riwayat ke mutabiq waqia bayan kya magar kaha : aey Allah! mere intihai boodhey waalidain they, main raat ke waqt un donon se pahley na ghar walon ko doodh pilaata tha, na maal ko (apni milkiyat ke ghulaamon ya maweshiyon ke un bachchon ko jinki apni maain na thin) doodh pilaataa tha aur (ye bhi) kaha : (meri chacha zaad) mujh se door rahi yahan tak ke aik qahat saali ka shikar ho gaee, wo mere paas aai to maine usey (so ke bajaey jo usney maangey they) aik so bees Dinar diye aur (teesrey shakhs ke waqiey mein) usne kaha : maine uski ujrat ko (kaashtkaari aur tijarat ke zariey) khub baar aawar banaya, yahan tak ke aisa karne se maal-maweshi bahut badh gaey aur phail gaey aur aakhir mein kaha : to wo chaltey huey ghaar se bahar aa gaey."
